en_142055_0	An 80-year-old mother of 15 from Gonewa village in Kallanchiya area, Mihintale shared her gloomy life story with Hiru News.
en_142055_1	She has given birth to 15 children.
en_142055_2	From them 11 are alive.
en_142055_3	However, this mother is not taken care of by her children.
en_142055_4	She lives in a makeshift house and eats what the villagers provide her.
en_142055_5	She is waiting humbly till someone comes to aide her during this vulnerable age. by Balasuriya Chinthaka
